       <Connector port=”8443″ ....>
	   
	   Scope of http authentication:
	   - <url-pattern>/*</url-pattern> : all (console and services)
	   - <url-pattern>/ws/*</url-pattern> : only services (wsdl, endpoint)
  -->
  <!--
  <security-constraint>
    <web-resource-collection>
